      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776001000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. preprocess / neutralize / bucket / rebalance 尺子是否都冻结\n2. neutralization policy / beta window / taxonomy reference 是否冻结\n3. train_variant_ledger 与 reject ledger 是否齐全且可解释\n4. frozen_signal_contract_reference 与 governable / non-governable axes 是否写清\n5. 是否没有用 test/backtest 结果回写 train 尺子\n6. signal 已冻结轴是否被错误重开为 train 搜索轴",
      "rawText": "1. preprocess / neutralize / bucket / rebalance 尺子是否都冻结\n2. neutralization policy / beta window / taxonomy reference 是否冻结\n3. train_variant_ledger 与 reject ledger 是否齐全且可解释\n4. frozen_signal_contract_reference 与 governable / non-governable axes 是否写清\n5. 是否没有用 test/backtest 结果回写 train 尺子\n6. signal 已冻结轴是否被错误重开为 train 搜索轴",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. preprocess / neutralize / bucket / rebalance 尺子是否都冻结\n2. neutralization policy / beta window / taxonomy reference 是否冻结\n3. train_variant_ledger 与 reject ledger 是否齐全且可解释\n4. frozen_signal_contract_reference 与 governable / non-governable axes 是否写清\n5. 是否没有用 test/backtest 结果回写 train 尺子\n6. signal 已冻结轴是否被错误重开为 train 搜索轴",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "hasTextLink": false
    },
