    },
    {
      "id": "why-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 540,
      "y": 420,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 90,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#92400e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a29",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1029,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 2029,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776001000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "因为 train 这一步最容易伪装成“受控搜索”，实际却偷偷把 signal 重新定义，或者只留下通过者。\nreview 的任务，就是把 train 限制成“冻结尺子与 admissible variants”的阶段，而不是挑胜者的阶段。",
      "rawText": "因为 train 这一步最容易伪装成“受控搜索”，实际却偷偷把 signal 重新定义，或者只留下通过者。\nreview 的任务，就是把 train 限制成“冻结尺子与 admissible variants”的阶段，而不是挑胜者的阶段。",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "因为 train 这一步最容易伪装成“受控搜索”，实际却偷偷把 signal 重新定义，或者只留下通过者。\nreview 的任务，就是把 train 限制成“冻结尺子与 admissible variants”的阶段，而不是挑胜者的阶段。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "hasTextLink": false
    },
