      "updated": 1776001000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. 五组都确认：preprocess / neutralization / ranking_bucket / rebalance / delivery\n2. csf_train_freeze.yaml 必须写 frozen_signal_contract_reference、train_governable_axes、non_governable_axes_after_signal、reject_rule\n3. 所有 variants 都有身份，所有 reject 都留原因\n4. signal 已冻结轴一旦想改，必须 reject 并说明应重开 csf_signal_ready\n5. 通过 review closure 后，才能进入 06 CSF Test Evidence",
      "rawText": "1. 五组都确认：preprocess / neutralization / ranking_bucket / rebalance / delivery\n2. csf_train_freeze.yaml 必须写 frozen_signal_contract_reference、train_governable_axes、non_governable_axes_after_signal、reject_rule\n3. 所有 variants 都有身份，所有 reject 都留原因\n4. signal 已冻结轴一旦想改，必须 reject 并说明应重开 csf_signal_ready\n5. 通过 review closure 后，才能进入 06 CSF Test Evidence",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. 五组都确认：preprocess / neutralization / ranking_bucket / rebalance / delivery\n2. csf_train_freeze.yaml 必须写 frozen_signal_contract_reference、train_governable_axes、non_governable_axes_after_signal、reject_rule\n3. 所有 variants 都有身份，所有 reject 都留原因\n4. signal 已冻结轴一旦想改，必须 reject 并说明应重开 csf_signal_ready\n5. 通过 review closure 后，才能进入 06 CSF Test Evidence",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "hasTextLink": false
    },
